results.title: The End of the Fantastic Four
The Terrible Triumph of Dr. Doom
War on the Thirty-Sixth Floor!
results.description: Still reeling from Sue's decision to stay with Namor last issue, the F.F. return to the Baxter Building and face the Frightful Four; Thundra shows up and helps our heroes defeat her former teammates; Namor begins another attack against humanity with Sue at his side.

results.title: The Fantastic Four Battle the Mad Thinker and His Awesome Android
The Man in the Mystery Mask!
Invasion from the 5th (Count it, the 5th!) Dimension
Havoc in the Hidden Land!
results.description: Sue Richards returns to the FF and Medusa leaves.

results.title: In One World--and Out the Other!
results.description: Alicia witnesses a battle between Arkon and The Thing from another dimension and confuses him for her Ben; Once she explains the situation to the real F.F., Ben borrows Lockjaw so he can travel through dimensions and find his namesake; Reed sells his interest in Fantastic Four Inc. to Interlocking Technologies.

results.title: Captain Marvel in The Big Bang
All the World Wars at Once!
The Shape of Things to Come!

results.title: Cry, the Bedeviled Planet!
results.description: The golden ape Gorr brings the FF to Counter Earth where they try to fight off the Destroyer before he calls Galactus to feed; They fail and the world eater shows up.

results.title: Captain America and The Red Skull
Counter-Earth Must Die--At the Hand of Galactus!
results.description: The FF try to find another planet to sacrifice so Galactus won't eat Counter Earth; After they are all captured, the Evolutionary decides to save his world by challenging Galactus in a fight to the death.

results.title: When Giants Walk the Sky!
results.description: The FF and Evolutionary face off against Galactus but are saved in the nick of time by--Impossible Man?
